            <title>[LU-16540] move ll_get_user_pages to ptlrpcd threads</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16540</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Moving ll_get_user_pages from the top level to running in the ptlrpcd context has the potential to significantly improve DIO performance (10% or more).&#160; This requires some code reorganization and some careful handling of vmpage assignment, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
